UniCredit May Provide Financing to Lactalis on Parmalat Bid, Ghizzoni Says

-- B y   J e f f   D o n o v a n   a n d   F l a v i a   R o t o n d i
-- 
2011-05-14T07:17:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-14/unicredit-may-provide-financing-to-lactalis-on-parmalat-bid-ghizzoni-says.html
UniCredit SpA (UCG)  may provide financing
for Groupe Lactalis’s bid to purchase the shares it doesn’t own
in  Parmalat SpA (PLT) , UniCredit Chief Executive Officer Federico
Ghizzoni told reporters at a conference today near Siena, Italy.
“We have been requested with other Italian banks; we’re
evaluating the situation and will decide in the next few days,”
he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Liefgreen at 
 dliefgreen@bloomberg.net  